ata-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614788\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 11, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nhj1665702629345.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nhj1665702629345.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nhj1665702629345.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nhj1665702629345\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Type of colors to display in the ColorList widget: <code class=\"ph codeph\">System</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Web</code> (default), <code class=\"ph codeph\">StrictWeb</code>, or <code class=\"ph codeph\">None</code>.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nhj1665702629345__p_d102689e1_d102690e1_d102691e1\">ColorType<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">System</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Web</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">StrictWeb</code> |\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">None</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__2\">Representation</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__1\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__2\">\n (default)\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__3\">Use the colors as defined in the application\n                        <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">System</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__2\">\n System\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__3\">Use system colors. The colors displayed are\n                     dependent on the system setup</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Web</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__2\">\n Web\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__3\">Use W3C standard web colors, plus numbered\n                     variations used in themes, such as <code class=\"ph codeph\">antiquewhite1</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">StrictWeb</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__3\">Use only W3C standard web colors. For more\n                     information, refer to <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/colors%2Fcolors_names.asp\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Color Names Supported on All Browsers</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">None</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nhj1665702629345__table_d12098e1_d12099e1_d12100e1__entry__3\">No colors are listed in the widget.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nhj1665702629345__section_xhb_cgb_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d229338e189\">Example:  Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"nhj1665702629345__pre_f2d_dgb_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(COLORS)=\"colortype=strictweb\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nhj1665702629345__section_vgq_dgb_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d229338e198\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gzs1665702629046.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gzs1665702629046.html\" title=\"The (ucolorlist) widget displays a list of system or web colors for selection in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called ColorList, which is mapped to ucolorlist.\">ucolorlist (ColorList)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614788\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614788\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Color Type (ColorType) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 11, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Type of colors to display in the ColorList widget: System , Web (default), StrictWeb , or None . ColorType = \" System | Web | StrictWeb | None \" Value Representation Description (default) Use the colors as defined in the application .ini file. System System Use system colors. The colors displayed are dependent on the system setup Web Web Use W3C standard web colors, plus numbered variations used in themes, such as antiquewhite1 StrictWeb Use only W3C standard web colors. For more information, refer to Color Names Supported on All Browsers None No colors are listed in the widget. Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(COLORS)=\"colortype=strictweb\" Copy Applies To ucolorlist (ColorList) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}